WEBVTT

01:34.080 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:41.920 --> 01:42.800
Eat up.

01:44.800 --> 01:46.120
Dad, you eat too.

01:46.200 --> 01:47.280
Alright, I will.

02:00.840 --> 02:02.040
What kind of new way
of eating is this, Dad?

02:03.800 --> 02:04.680
It's good for digestion.

02:05.360 --> 02:07.720
Is your stomach upset?
Are you feeling unwell?

02:08.560 --> 02:09.600
I'm fine.

02:10.120 --> 02:11.560
Eating like this will keep me healthy.

02:12.640 --> 02:13.680
Hurry up and eat.

02:13.760 --> 02:14.800
It's getting cold.

02:24.880 --> 02:27.280
- Hello, Dad?
- Hello, Jiang.

02:27.360 --> 02:28.920
Why was this business trip so long?

02:29.000 --> 02:30.640
You didn't even come back
for my birthday yesterday.

02:32.080 --> 02:33.200
I'm sorry.

02:35.000 --> 02:35.880
I'll be back soon.

02:37.200 --> 02:38.280
Almost home.

02:39.080 --> 02:40.320
Then, hurry up and come back.

02:42.160 --> 02:43.200
Jiang,

02:44.040 --> 02:46.520
did you eat the cake Mom bought for you?

02:47.440 --> 02:48.400
I did.

02:48.480 --> 02:49.640
I even ate your share.

02:51.520 --> 02:52.400
All right.

02:53.720 --> 02:55.040
- All right.
- Okay then.

02:55.120 --> 02:56.200
Go ahead with your business.

02:56.720 --> 02:57.880
Come home soon.

02:59.120 --> 03:01.280
Okay. Bye-bye.

03:10.920 --> 03:12.600
My dear Jiang,

03:13.840 --> 03:15.520
you have to grow up well.

03:17.920 --> 03:19.560
Just like before,

03:21.240 --> 03:23.560
be happy every single day.

03:27.200 --> 03:29.120
And take care of Mom.

03:30.880 --> 03:33.000
You're the person closest to her.

03:36.080 --> 03:36.960
Alright.

03:38.160 --> 03:39.120
Yuandong.

03:42.680 --> 03:44.040
Remember this.

03:44.600 --> 03:46.160
You are

03:46.240 --> 03:47.840
Jiang's only support.

04:02.600 --> 04:03.880
4,071 DAYS

04:03.960 --> 04:05.840
NANWU TV STATION

04:05.920 --> 04:07.400
Thank you for the interview.

04:07.480 --> 04:09.920
Miss, it was really nice talking to you.

04:10.000 --> 04:11.280
I don't feel as scared now.

04:12.680 --> 04:15.840
We shouldn't have to please others
or stay silent when we're bullied.

04:15.920 --> 04:16.920
We were born

04:17.000 --> 04:18.920
not to be anyone's pleaser.

04:19.000 --> 04:20.040
We should learn to be kind to ourselves.

04:22.520 --> 04:25.240
Once the video is edited,
we'll send it to you.

04:25.320 --> 04:26.480
Sounds good.

04:29.280 --> 04:30.360
Make sure to leave them our contact info.

04:30.440 --> 04:31.280
Got it.

04:33.760 --> 04:34.720
Hello?

04:35.240 --> 04:36.360
Are you done?

04:36.440 --> 04:37.400
Almost.

04:38.000 --> 04:39.760
Didn't you have a follow-up checkup today?

04:39.840 --> 04:40.920
I had it earlier.

04:41.520 --> 04:43.720
The doctor even stitched a dragon
on my wound.

04:43.800 --> 04:45.280
Doesn't that hurt even more?

04:46.480 --> 04:47.480
Why are you so serious?

04:48.680 --> 04:49.800
Are you off work yet?

04:50.360 --> 04:51.320
I'll come pick you up.

04:51.920 --> 04:52.960
Wait for me like a good girl.

04:57.120 --> 04:58.280
Jiang!

05:00.960 --> 05:02.000
Jiang!

05:05.960 --> 05:07.520
Can you come here for a sec?

05:08.440 --> 05:10.240
I have a few words to say.

05:10.840 --> 05:11.760
Jiang!

05:18.320 --> 05:20.360
Uncle Zheng and I just had a meal nearby.

05:20.960 --> 05:22.400
He went back to the office to work.

05:22.480 --> 05:24.560
Since your workplace is nearby,

05:24.640 --> 05:25.840
I stopped by.

05:28.960 --> 05:30.240
Jiang, it's your birthday today.

05:31.000 --> 05:32.400
Can we talk for a bit?

05:33.160 --> 05:34.640
- I still have things to do later.
- I…

05:34.720 --> 05:36.600
I won't take up too much of your time.

05:36.680 --> 05:37.880
Just…

05:37.960 --> 05:41.240
Just give me a chance.
Let me wish you a happy birthday,

05:43.160 --> 05:44.000
okay?

05:53.320 --> 05:54.280
Jiang.

05:54.840 --> 05:56.640
Let me order you a cake.

05:56.720 --> 05:58.200
What flavor do you want?

05:58.280 --> 05:59.160
No need.

06:00.680 --> 06:01.520
Hello.

06:01.600 --> 06:03.400
Two strawberry cakes, please.

06:03.480 --> 06:04.600
Alright, just a moment.

06:08.600 --> 06:10.720
- It's rare for us to--
- What do you want to talk about?

06:15.000 --> 06:17.320
I never imagined that Che Xingde
would turn out to be this kind of person.

06:17.400 --> 06:19.040
I wrote that news report.

06:25.920 --> 06:26.920
Jiang.

06:29.360 --> 06:30.480
Back then…

06:32.320 --> 06:34.240
did he manage to do anything bad to you?

06:40.520 --> 06:41.720
Regarding that question…

06:43.720 --> 06:45.000
How am I supposed to answer?

06:48.120 --> 06:50.040
But I am really scared.

06:50.120 --> 06:51.800
Mom, please take me home.

06:51.880 --> 06:54.680
Please! I was so scared!

06:56.120 --> 06:57.760
I'm begging you!

06:57.840 --> 07:00.840
Jiang, don't cry. Listen to me.

07:00.920 --> 07:03.280
I'll talk to your Uncle Wen properly.

07:03.360 --> 07:05.000
Don't worry. I'm hanging up now.

07:05.600 --> 07:06.720
Stop crying.

07:18.560 --> 07:19.440
It's been so long.

07:25.440 --> 07:26.520
Jiang.

07:27.120 --> 07:29.200
Are you…
Are you misunderstanding the situation?

07:29.920 --> 07:32.320
Your Uncle Che is a good man.

07:32.400 --> 07:34.480
He would never do such a thing.

07:40.560 --> 07:42.520
It's my fault.

07:47.400 --> 07:49.080
I…

07:49.160 --> 07:52.680
I didn't pay enough attention
to you back then.

07:53.520 --> 07:55.760
I thought with your Uncle Wen
watching over you,

07:55.840 --> 07:57.160
nothing bad would happen.

08:00.920 --> 08:02.240
It's all my fault.

08:06.920 --> 08:07.840
Jiang.

08:11.760 --> 08:14.040
I'm not asking for your forgiveness.

08:16.400 --> 08:18.440
I just want to see you sometimes.

08:19.760 --> 08:20.840
Is that okay?

08:29.320 --> 08:31.320
Honestly, no matter how
Uncle Wen's family treated me,

08:33.320 --> 08:34.840
it never really hurt me.

08:37.320 --> 08:39.159
They had no obligation to take care of me.

08:39.679 --> 08:41.400
And they certainly had no reason…

08:44.800 --> 08:45.760
to be kind to me.

08:56.080 --> 08:58.440
Excuse me. Where should I put the cakes?

08:59.240 --> 09:01.760
Uh… Just leave it over there. Thank you.

09:01.840 --> 09:03.080
Alright.

09:08.280 --> 09:09.560
It's you.

09:12.120 --> 09:13.880
You made me miserable.

09:15.560 --> 09:17.840
You made me doubt myself.

09:21.520 --> 09:24.680
Why, in this world, does the mother
who should love me most

09:32.400 --> 09:33.880
not love me at all?

09:33.960 --> 09:35.200
No.

09:38.400 --> 09:39.320
That's not true.

09:39.840 --> 09:40.760
It's because…

09:40.840 --> 09:42.760
It's because you had a new family,

09:44.320 --> 09:46.440
and you had to think about yourself more.

09:53.000 --> 09:55.880
When you sent me to Grandma's house,
I should have realized it.

10:05.520 --> 10:08.600
When you kept ignoring me
for the sake of your new family,

10:09.560 --> 10:12.240
when I begged you for help
but you chose not to hear me,

10:19.080 --> 10:21.720
when I had nowhere to go
and you didn't even care,

10:21.800 --> 10:23.400
I should have
understood everything by then.

10:27.040 --> 10:29.280
IN MEMORY OF MY LATE FATHER, WEN LIANGZHE

10:38.520 --> 10:39.440
It's good.

10:40.120 --> 10:42.080
I just feel like having something sweet.

10:43.720 --> 10:45.320
How's your health been lately?

10:45.400 --> 10:46.400
Pretty good.

10:47.720 --> 10:48.880
You're always so busy with work.

10:48.960 --> 10:50.080
Just focus on your job.

10:50.680 --> 10:51.600
Jiang.

10:51.680 --> 10:53.400
I just made some tremella soup.

10:53.480 --> 10:55.360
- Come have some.
- Yeah, try some.

10:56.280 --> 10:57.720
I have homework to do.

10:58.400 --> 11:00.160
Why didn't you greet your uncle?

11:00.720 --> 11:01.960
It's okay.

11:02.040 --> 11:04.720
Yifan is still not used to it.

11:04.800 --> 11:06.000
Don't put her on the spot.

11:08.640 --> 11:10.520
Jiang, I want to discuss
something with you.

11:12.800 --> 11:15.760
But first, let's agree not to argue.

11:16.320 --> 11:17.600
Keep our emotions in check.

11:18.160 --> 11:19.200
The main thing is,

11:20.320 --> 11:21.560
I can't get emotional right now.

11:22.400 --> 11:23.360
Why?

11:25.200 --> 11:26.240
I'm pregnant.

11:27.480 --> 11:28.440
Uh…

11:28.520 --> 11:29.800
Work is calling me.

11:29.880 --> 11:31.200
I need to take this.

11:34.200 --> 11:35.960
Have you already forgotten Dad?

11:40.720 --> 11:43.680
I don't expect you to remember him
for the rest of your life like I do.

11:46.280 --> 11:47.520
You can remarry,

11:49.640 --> 11:51.120
you can have new children…

11:55.200 --> 11:56.720
but not now.

12:04.440 --> 12:05.560
Your stepfather…

12:06.360 --> 12:07.920
He has been

12:08.880 --> 12:10.120
seeing someone else.

12:17.240 --> 12:18.280
Before,

12:20.400 --> 12:22.200
we argued about it a few times.

12:25.600 --> 12:28.080
He promised me he wouldn't do it again.

12:29.080 --> 12:30.240
Kejia probably…

12:31.800 --> 12:34.480
probably just wanted you to come back
to keep me company. That's why…

12:35.760 --> 12:38.000
That's why she called you home.

12:38.080 --> 12:40.080
Is this history repeating itself?

12:40.600 --> 12:42.240
What happened to me back then,

12:44.080 --> 12:46.200
you're experiencing it now.

12:49.200 --> 12:51.920
Neither of us was ever truly chosen.

12:54.800 --> 12:56.680
We were both abandoned,

12:56.760 --> 12:58.200
left behind.

13:27.880 --> 13:29.920
I've been thinking about…

13:33.360 --> 13:35.640
how to handle our relationship.

13:36.680 --> 13:38.960
I never deleted your contact info.

13:41.800 --> 13:43.600
I was afraid that
if something happened to you,

13:44.680 --> 13:45.920
I wouldn't know what to do.

13:49.640 --> 13:51.440
But later, I realized I was overthinking.

13:56.240 --> 13:57.480
All these years,

13:58.760 --> 14:00.360
you ignored me completely.

14:01.440 --> 14:03.040
And yet I still managed to live.

14:08.280 --> 14:10.440
I never said these things before.

14:12.400 --> 14:16.320
I kept them buried inside,
like a weight on my chest.

14:19.960 --> 14:20.880
After today,

14:22.640 --> 14:24.640
I'm deleting
all my ways of contacting you.

14:31.040 --> 14:32.240
I hope…

14:37.320 --> 14:39.800
I hope that in your mind, your daughter

14:43.080 --> 14:46.600
had already been killed
by Che Xingde…

14:48.960 --> 14:49.800
that night.

16:04.640 --> 16:05.600
Where are we going?

16:06.880 --> 16:08.760
Home, to celebrate your birthday?

16:14.880 --> 16:17.440
Can I make a birthday wish now?

16:22.880 --> 16:24.120
If…

16:25.560 --> 16:28.440
next summer is still just as long,

16:32.520 --> 16:33.640
you will propose to me,

16:35.360 --> 16:36.360
will you?

16:42.520 --> 16:43.400
I will.

16:54.760 --> 16:55.640
Anything else?

16:56.920 --> 16:58.720
- Can I make another?
- Of course.

16:59.480 --> 17:00.400
You can.

17:02.400 --> 17:03.560
Then…

17:06.000 --> 17:08.160
I hope the summer after next

17:10.040 --> 17:11.040
will be just as long.

17:13.520 --> 17:15.599
Isn't that the same wish

17:15.680 --> 17:16.640
as the last one?

17:17.680 --> 17:19.240
You're really saving me the trouble.

17:21.119 --> 17:22.680
Every year, your wishes

17:23.480 --> 17:24.760
are always the things I want to do.

17:26.800 --> 17:30.080
All my wishes from our first year
as roommates have come true.

17:31.200 --> 17:33.200
Are you talking about work?

17:33.280 --> 17:36.160
Or… that you wanted me
to be your boyfriend?

17:40.480 --> 17:41.400
Any more?

17:42.600 --> 17:45.000
Are you giving me three wishes?

17:49.520 --> 17:50.520
Then…

17:51.600 --> 17:52.800
carry me on your back?

17:57.560 --> 17:59.760
Forget it. Let's go.

18:03.400 --> 18:04.680
Come on.

18:08.200 --> 18:09.400
Hurry up.

18:13.960 --> 18:15.240
Fine, just for a bit.

18:20.120 --> 18:21.120
Anything else?

18:26.160 --> 18:27.160
Give me a smile.

18:28.280 --> 18:29.320
Why?

18:30.600 --> 18:32.520
Why do you always avoid smiling at me?

18:33.600 --> 18:34.560
You look so cute when you smile.

18:35.520 --> 18:36.840
Don't use that word to describe me.

18:43.440 --> 18:44.400
But…

18:46.160 --> 18:47.920
you look so good when you smile.

18:48.960 --> 18:49.960
Could you?

18:55.560 --> 18:58.320
Every time you smile,
the little mole near your eye

18:59.200 --> 19:00.880
is like a dancing ant.

19:02.880 --> 19:04.600
Like a dancing ant?

19:06.320 --> 19:08.560
Alright, I'll take that as a compliment.

19:10.080 --> 19:11.600
Either way,
you're only allowed to smile for me.

19:12.120 --> 19:14.040
When did you become so controlling?

19:15.160 --> 19:16.840
You told me to make wishes.

19:19.920 --> 19:20.960
Fine.

19:21.560 --> 19:22.440
Anything else?

19:46.120 --> 19:47.440
What's wrong? Still thinking?

19:58.160 --> 19:59.640
No one loves me anymore.

20:03.080 --> 20:04.040
Only you.

20:10.720 --> 20:11.840
I only love you.

20:15.120 --> 20:16.440
From the very beginning,

20:18.320 --> 20:20.760
step by step, we walked here.

20:22.000 --> 20:23.360
We'll keep walking

20:24.600 --> 20:25.560
into the future.

20:31.720 --> 20:32.680
Wen Shuangjiang,

20:34.640 --> 20:35.640
make another wish.

20:41.200 --> 20:42.520
I don't have any more wishes.

20:44.160 --> 20:45.400
You can have mine.

20:51.600 --> 20:52.520
Then I wish…

20:55.960 --> 20:56.840
I wish that besides me,

20:59.600 --> 21:00.920
there will be many people who love you.

21:41.120 --> 21:43.240
Sitting for so long made my back ache.

21:45.200 --> 21:46.800
It's not like you were the one driving.

21:46.880 --> 21:48.200
It's a six-hour journey!

21:48.280 --> 21:49.520
That was exhausting.

22:00.040 --> 22:01.280
Grandma, is this the place?

22:01.920 --> 22:04.000
It looks like
there are a lot more trees now.

22:04.080 --> 22:05.920
Haoan, come here.

22:13.800 --> 22:14.880
Look.

22:16.040 --> 22:17.160
This is the spot

22:17.680 --> 22:20.440
where their car crashed
all those years ago.

22:21.600 --> 22:24.200
They said it was because
the car was going too fast.

22:24.280 --> 22:26.120
It skidded and went off the road.

22:27.160 --> 22:28.080
Back then,

22:28.960 --> 22:30.800
how could we have

22:30.880 --> 22:33.080
let a little kid like you

22:33.160 --> 22:35.680
see all of this firsthand?

22:37.920 --> 22:39.200
Your grandpa and I…

22:39.720 --> 22:42.160
We nearly passed out.

22:42.800 --> 22:44.720
It was unbearable!

22:45.880 --> 22:47.800
It was my idea back then

22:48.520 --> 22:49.920
to keep you at home.

22:50.000 --> 22:53.840
I thought that would be
the safest place for you.

22:54.560 --> 22:57.040
But I never imagined not telling you

22:57.880 --> 23:00.480
would affect you for so many years.

23:01.440 --> 23:05.120
At first, I thought it was okay.
Maybe everyone just needed time.

23:05.640 --> 23:07.360
But as the years passed,
I started wondering.

23:07.440 --> 23:08.680
Was it my fault?

23:08.760 --> 23:10.040
I began blaming myself.

23:10.120 --> 23:11.280
It must've been
because I wasn't good enough,

23:11.360 --> 23:13.080
because I didn't meet your expectations.

23:13.160 --> 23:15.280
Everything started with me.

23:15.360 --> 23:17.560
I was the problem.
I deserved to be abandoned, didn't I?

23:18.800 --> 23:20.880
Why would you think that?

23:22.200 --> 23:24.560
No one has ever stopped loving you.

23:24.640 --> 23:25.800
All this time,

23:25.880 --> 23:28.360
you and your brother have been

23:28.440 --> 23:30.160
the most precious to your grandpa and me!

23:30.880 --> 23:31.960
Alright.

23:32.960 --> 23:34.000
Let us

23:34.080 --> 23:36.400
just forget all these painful memories

23:36.480 --> 23:37.640
and let them go.

23:40.440 --> 23:42.520
Have you ever wondered

23:42.600 --> 23:45.960
why your name is Haoan?

23:48.080 --> 23:51.240
Your father's name was Su Haoyang.

23:51.320 --> 23:54.240
Your mother's name was Hu Jiaan.

23:54.320 --> 23:56.600
Your father's second character

23:56.680 --> 23:58.640
and your mother's third character…

23:58.720 --> 24:00.640
That's how you got Haoan.

24:00.720 --> 24:02.440
You and your brother

24:02.520 --> 24:05.280
were both the loves of their lives.

24:06.280 --> 24:08.840
They didn't love him more,

24:08.920 --> 24:12.040
and they didn't love you any less.

24:37.640 --> 24:39.000
All these years,

24:40.840 --> 24:43.000
I tried my best to please everyone.

24:45.520 --> 24:47.560
But the hardest person
to comfort was myself.

24:48.080 --> 24:50.200
Those who can't forgive themselves
suffer most.

24:52.080 --> 24:53.880
We need to be kinder to ourselves.

24:58.800 --> 24:59.640
Dad.

25:00.880 --> 25:01.760
Mom.

25:04.080 --> 25:04.920
Brother.

25:06.520 --> 25:07.840
All these years,

25:11.400 --> 25:12.560
I've grown up.

25:15.440 --> 25:16.440
Can you see me?

25:19.840 --> 25:21.000
The old me

25:21.880 --> 25:22.840
was afraid of loss.

25:24.720 --> 25:26.040
I always relied on others.

25:27.640 --> 25:29.000
But now…

25:31.800 --> 25:34.240
I finally understand
what it means to be loved.

25:40.400 --> 25:42.120
I will keep living my life

25:42.720 --> 25:44.200
with confidence.

25:45.000 --> 25:47.600
And I will take care
of Grandpa and Grandma for you.

25:48.120 --> 25:49.040
You can rest easy.

25:52.880 --> 25:56.720
Don't worry. Your grandma and I
don't need you to take care of us.

25:57.320 --> 25:59.760
Your grandpa agreed
to go on a road trip with me.

25:59.840 --> 26:01.320
That's great, Grandma!

26:01.400 --> 26:04.080
Grandpa is finally willing
to make your dream come true.

26:04.160 --> 26:05.040
Let's go right away.

26:05.640 --> 26:06.520
Time to hit the road!

26:07.280 --> 26:08.320
Where are we going?

26:09.080 --> 26:10.520
On a road trip!

26:11.200 --> 26:12.720
But first, we need to go home,

26:12.800 --> 26:16.240
get in my car, and then we can leave.

26:16.840 --> 26:17.680
Then, why are you calling Ma?

26:18.560 --> 26:21.000
This is a trip just for the two of us.
Why bring him along?

26:21.080 --> 26:22.360
He's the driver.

26:22.960 --> 26:24.640
I don't want that!
Just the two of us are enough!

26:25.680 --> 26:26.920
Only us?

26:27.000 --> 26:29.720
Well then, I should call Laughter.

26:33.280 --> 26:34.280
What's wrong with you?

26:35.040 --> 26:37.480
Why are you calling Laughter?

26:37.560 --> 26:38.680
Of course, I have to!

26:38.760 --> 26:42.000
I have to call her.
She and I are going on a road trip.

26:42.080 --> 26:43.240
Who's Laughter?

26:44.040 --> 26:45.720
Laughter is you!

26:46.640 --> 26:47.560
I'm just messing with you.

26:47.640 --> 26:49.320
Alright. Let's head out.

26:49.400 --> 26:50.840
Come on. Let's go!

26:50.920 --> 26:51.880
Let's go.

26:55.400 --> 26:56.560
This feels great.

26:59.920 --> 27:01.040
Get in the car!

27:21.280 --> 27:22.440
Where are you now?

27:22.960 --> 27:24.840
Our program starts at seven.

27:24.920 --> 27:27.800
If I don't reply later,
that means I'm already on stage.

27:27.880 --> 27:29.360
Ask Fu Zhuang to bring you in.

27:30.760 --> 27:31.680
Alright.

27:34.200 --> 27:35.040
Try it.

27:35.120 --> 27:36.080
Hurry up.

27:39.360 --> 27:40.520
Still not working?

27:47.400 --> 27:49.720
Yan! There's an urgent matter for you.

27:49.800 --> 27:51.920
Here's the deal.
A few key projects ran into problems.

27:52.000 --> 27:53.440
We need you to fix them.

27:53.520 --> 27:54.440
You two can't handle it?

27:54.520 --> 27:55.640
Yan,

27:55.720 --> 27:57.360
you can solve it in ten minutes.

27:57.440 --> 27:59.520
If they try,
they'll be stuck for three days.

27:59.600 --> 28:00.720
- Get to the conference room!
- Move!

28:00.800 --> 28:02.280
- Yeah, work!
- Hurry up!

28:02.360 --> 28:04.360
- Yan, quick!
- Move!

28:04.440 --> 28:06.520
HELLO NANWU, HAPPY NEW YEAR
NANWU TV STATION

28:06.600 --> 28:07.440
Zhen Yu.

28:07.520 --> 28:08.440
Zhen Yu.

28:09.400 --> 28:11.040
- Yang.
- Yifan.

28:11.120 --> 28:13.600
Can I ask about my performance?
What's my lineup number?

28:14.360 --> 28:15.520
You're third.

28:15.600 --> 28:16.560
That early?

28:16.640 --> 28:18.040
Not ready yet?

28:18.120 --> 28:19.120
No…

28:19.840 --> 28:21.280
I'm worried my boyfriend won't make it.

28:22.880 --> 28:25.520
I never thought you, of all people,
would agree to perform.

28:25.600 --> 28:26.480
So, that's why.

28:27.960 --> 28:30.920
Well, if he doesn't make it,

28:31.000 --> 28:32.800
can I trouble you
to record a video for me?

28:32.880 --> 28:35.360
No problem.
I'll make sure you look amazing!

28:35.960 --> 28:37.720
- Get ready.
- Thanks.

28:42.480 --> 28:43.920
Will you make it in time?

28:44.000 --> 28:45.480
I only want to dance for you.

29:04.720 --> 29:07.640
Stunning!

29:19.000 --> 29:21.360
Stunning!

29:46.640 --> 29:49.000
LOOKING AHEAD, BUILDING DREAMS
NANWU TV STATION

30:03.280 --> 30:04.480
You're up next.

30:04.560 --> 30:05.600
Nervous?

30:06.520 --> 30:07.560
You got this!

30:24.280 --> 30:26.480
Fu Zhuang! Has it started?

30:26.560 --> 30:27.840
Almost.

30:27.920 --> 30:28.800
Why are you just getting here?

30:28.880 --> 30:31.120
Let me tell you.
Yifan has been working so hard.

30:31.200 --> 30:32.040
Every day after work,

30:32.120 --> 30:33.680
she goes to the meeting room alone
to practice dancing.

30:34.280 --> 30:36.920
You know how long she's been practicing.
Why haven't you gone to keep her company?

30:37.000 --> 30:38.120
By herself?

30:38.200 --> 30:40.440
Wasn't she singing with Su Tian?

30:40.520 --> 30:42.000
Singing?

30:42.080 --> 30:44.360
Where did you hear that?
Come on. Let's go!

30:44.440 --> 30:47.560
What an incredible magic performance!
Everyone saw that, right?

30:47.640 --> 30:50.800
Now, moving on.
I'd like to ask everyone to quiet down.

30:50.880 --> 30:51.760
Up next

30:51.840 --> 30:53.160
is a special performance

30:53.240 --> 30:55.520
from the First News team.

30:55.600 --> 30:57.520
A ballet piece from The Nutcracker,

30:57.600 --> 30:59.280
performed by Wen Yifan.

30:59.880 --> 31:02.880
She has been preparing
for this piece for a long time.

31:02.960 --> 31:06.120
I believe you'll all enjoy
a stunning performance.

31:55.080 --> 31:57.600
Did you use to love watching me dance?

32:58.200 --> 32:59.800
Yifan!

33:30.480 --> 33:31.760
When did you get here?

33:32.440 --> 33:34.480
Just as your performance started.

33:42.880 --> 33:43.720
You're sweating.

33:44.560 --> 33:45.600
Be careful not to catch a cold.

33:47.880 --> 33:49.800
Why aren't you saying anything
about my performance?

33:52.360 --> 33:54.800
Why haven't you danced in so long?
You danced beautifully.

33:55.680 --> 33:56.720
Really?

33:58.040 --> 33:59.840
It's been so long
since I properly practiced.

33:59.920 --> 34:02.080
Before, I was only demonstrating
simple moves for the kids.

34:03.160 --> 34:06.320
Performing a full piece again
made me a little nervous.

34:06.400 --> 34:08.679
It didn't look unprofessional, did it?

34:08.760 --> 34:11.679
Don't be so modest.
That was anything but unprofessional.

34:13.159 --> 34:15.520
Are you watching
the rest of the performances?

34:17.000 --> 34:19.639
I already watched the one I wanted to.

34:21.080 --> 34:22.480
Then wait for me a sec. I'll go change.

34:30.120 --> 34:31.360
You look great in this dress.

34:39.639 --> 34:41.880
I never told you I would dance.

34:43.159 --> 34:44.400
Why didn't you?

34:44.480 --> 34:46.320
Because this was
my New Year's gift to you.

34:49.639 --> 34:50.920
I'm glad I got to see it.

34:52.920 --> 34:54.320
When are we moving?

34:54.400 --> 34:55.360
Is the apartment finished?

34:55.960 --> 34:56.800
That depends.

34:57.320 --> 34:58.680
Whenever you have time.

34:59.640 --> 35:01.120
Before March…

35:01.720 --> 35:04.040
After New Year's, then.
I'll be freer around that time.

35:04.800 --> 35:05.720
Alright.

35:06.480 --> 35:09.600
Should we buy some boxes first
for packing?

35:09.680 --> 35:12.960
Just pack up your own things.
I'll handle everything else.

35:37.680 --> 35:38.560
Why is the light off?

35:57.560 --> 35:58.880
I really want to hide you away.

36:01.000 --> 36:02.080
Wen Shuangjiang,

36:02.760 --> 36:04.200
I feel like…

36:05.360 --> 36:07.120
I've changed since being with you.

36:10.760 --> 36:13.040
I've become selfish, possessive.

36:14.480 --> 36:16.640
Back on that stage,

36:17.440 --> 36:19.040
you were shining.

36:20.760 --> 36:22.840
But I couldn't bear
to let anyone else see it.

36:26.760 --> 36:29.760
I want you to shine in my world alone.

36:32.960 --> 36:34.320
But I know I can't do that.

36:35.840 --> 36:37.040
You should…

36:38.680 --> 36:41.400
You should let them see you.
See how incredible you are.

37:13.960 --> 37:14.920
Wen Shuangjiang…

37:17.800 --> 37:18.640
Time to pay your debt.

37:26.960 --> 37:28.200
Don't pull it.

37:28.280 --> 37:29.240
Why not?

37:29.320 --> 37:31.000
It's all one piece. You'll ruin it.

38:26.440 --> 38:28.280
YIHE DAILY, RESIGINATION LETTER

38:28.360 --> 38:29.960
His wife came to make a scene?

38:30.040 --> 38:31.000
You didn't do anything. Why do you care?

38:31.080 --> 38:31.920
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

38:32.000 --> 38:34.960
Or are you actually afraid
of people talking behind your back?

38:35.800 --> 38:38.120
I didn't do anything.
I'm not afraid of misunderstandings.

38:38.200 --> 38:39.880
Then why quit?

38:43.880 --> 38:46.600
Because there's nothing here
worth staying for.

38:48.400 --> 38:51.240
So, will you take a break?
Or find another job?

38:51.320 --> 38:54.400
- There will be other coworkers, other men…
- I'll return to Nanwu.

38:57.760 --> 38:59.080
I suddenly really want to go back there.

39:44.800 --> 39:46.840
STRAWBERRY CAKE

40:11.600 --> 40:12.440
Hello.

40:12.520 --> 40:15.200
I'd like the cake in the middle.
The one covered in strawberries.

40:15.280 --> 40:16.320
How much?

40:17.080 --> 40:18.560
Eighty-eight yuan. Scan here to pay.

40:24.880 --> 40:26.400
Could you do me a favor?

40:30.960 --> 40:33.640
Could you give this
to the girl in blue over there?

40:35.960 --> 40:37.280
Just tell her

40:37.360 --> 40:38.360
it's a store promotion.

40:38.440 --> 40:40.160
If she posts about it,
she can have it for free.

40:40.840 --> 40:42.200
- Thank you.
- It's nothing.

40:54.080 --> 40:55.280
Hi, miss.

40:55.360 --> 40:56.880
This is our store's new product.

40:56.960 --> 40:58.000
No, thank you.

40:58.080 --> 41:01.200
Actually, if you help us
promote it by posting online,

41:01.280 --> 41:03.400
this cake is free!

41:04.640 --> 41:05.760
Just remember to post it!

44:14.240 --> 44:15.360
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

44:15.440 --> 44:16.520
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
